episodes.title: Why Trump administration no more Epstein files will be released
episodes.description: The announcement came as the Justice Department released 3 million pages on the late convicted sex offender. Conan Nolan reports for the NBC4 News at 6 p.m. on Friday, Jan. 30, 2026.

episodes.title: Protest held outside Hollywood restaurant turns violent
episodes.description: A clash outside a Hollywood restaurant turned violent between protesters and patrons. Anastassia Olmos reports for the NBC4 News on Feb. 17, 2024.
